Guidelines CPR&ECC de la AHA.October 20, 2020 - Volume 142, Issue 16_suppl_2 https://www.ahajournals.org/toc/circ/142/16_suppl_2?utm_campaign=sciencenews20-21&utm_source=science-news&utm_medium=phd-link&utm_content=phd10-21-20

BIBLIOGRAFIA RECOMENDADA:
CARAVACA CABALLERO, ANA: MANUAL DE PRIMEROS AUXILIOS ARAN EDICIONES, S.A., 2009
